cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.RO 

The paper deals with crowd counting in videos using convolutional neural networks and spatial transformer modules. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a new method for crowd counting, which involves the use of a spatial transformer module, which falls under the category of machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG and cs.AI). The paper also deals with video processing and analysis, which falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper proposes a method for crowd counting in dynamic scenes, which involves the use of a spatial transformer module, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO).
